Articles.Content:
Hi everyone, I am not very sure about this topic, is this the right place to post albums ? Anyway It's been a while that I wanted to share my favourite crafts and pictures I made in game since I began playing so here I go .

( I also wanted to say a huge thanks to Beale, his parts mods Tantares and Tantares LV kept giving me ideas and you can find his pieces in a lot of my pictures )

 

As a lot of the crafts shown here have been made years ago in older versions of KSP, using old versions of mods I can't promise you all the parts are still available, but I will do my best to answer if some of you guys have any questions And thanks a lot for whose have paid attention to my topic ! I felt like I had to share how much fun this community gave me through modding and help !

 

Edited May 18, 2016 by spacecookie
